The paper discusses the foundations and methodologies of intrusion detection systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on the use of fuzzy logic and genetic algorithms, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of these techniques in improving the capability of computer systems, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
